"""Identify the controller by blinking its LEDs."""
with expected_protocol(ik.thorlabs.APTMotorController, [init_kdc101[0],
    ThorLabsPacket(message_id=ThorLabsCommands.MOD_IDENTIFY, param1=0,
    param2=0, dest=80, source=1, data=None).pack()], [init_kdc101[1]], sep=''
    ) as apt:
    apt.identify()
